title: Save.My.Bakery.S01E01.WS.DSR.x264-NY2
description:
Family-owned bakeries used to occupy vital places on Main Streets everywhere, but these days they are more often rundown than thriving. Enter renowned cake maestro Kerry Vincent, who answers the desperate call of bakery owners in over their heads. Armed with a spot of tea and a no-nonsense approach, Kerry gives each place a makeover from the inside out, turning stale pastries into delectable desserts and outdated decor into a brand-new, inviting space Ã¢â‚¬â€ but most importantly, transforming the families who have kept these businesses open.




Save my Bakery - Season 1, Episode 1



Viking Pastries

Viking Pastries of Ardmore, Pa., was the most successful game in town, but that all changed when the owners were struck by a family tragedy. Since then, the bakery has lost its heart and soul and the family has been relying on aging clientele and old school recipes to keep in business. On the brink of closing, Kerry Vincent swoops in to give Viking Pastries' products a facelift that will appeal to the local college community, glittery sprinkles and all.




Original Air Date: 19-Mar-2014
